Usage: reportShifter [-help] [-cell <string>] [-from <string>] [-highlight]
                     [-outfile <string>] [-to <string>]

-help                         # Prints out the command usage
-cell <string>                # cell name (string, optional)
-from <string>                # from power domain (string, optional)
-highlight                    # highlight isolation insts (bool, optional)
-outfile <string>             # output file (string, optional)
-to <string>                  # to power domain (string, optional)